{
  "texts": [
    "For future directions to take with this work, we suggest a more comprehensive analysis of both base models and compression techniques.",
    "We primarily investigated the WANDA pruning of 7billion parameter models.",
    "However, it would be prudent to check whether these trends hold for larger models.",
    "Similarly, we chose this compression technique for its high efficacy and ease of usage, but exploring other means of compressing would provide a more robust understanding of the effects on safety.",
    "Below we present the detailed safety results for Vicuna 1.3 and Mistral Instruct v0.2"
  ]
}